OL,3,CMore than 1,000 South West bus drivers
OL,4,Cvote to strike in September
OL,6,FMore than 1,000 First West of England
OL,7,Fbus drivers have voted for strike
OL,8,Faction in a dispute over pay.
OL,10,FThe strikes will take place at the
OL,11,Fstart of September and are set to
OL,12,Fimpact services including Bristol,
OL,13,FBath, Weston-super-Mare and Wells, the
OL,14,FUnite union has announced.
OL,16,FIt will coincide with the start of the
OL,17,Fnew school term, causing disruption
OL,18,Ffor thousands of schoolchildren, along
OL,19,Fwith commuters.
