OL,3,CMore than 1,000 South West bus drivers
OL,4,Cvote to strike in September
OL,6,FThe union has rejected the latest 2-
OL,7,Fyear pay deal from the operator.
OL,9,FBosses argue the offer was fair and
OL,10,F"significantly above the rate of
OL,11,Finflation", but striking union members
OL,12,Fsay they have been left with 'no
OL,13,Fchoice' but to take action.
OL,15,FThe industrial action is due to take
OL,16,Fplace in Bristol, Bath, Weston-super-
OL,17,FMare and Wells from 4 to 8 September,
OL,18,Ffollowed by further strikes on 16 to
OL,19,F19 September.
