OL,3,CMore than 1,000 South West bus drivers
OL,4,Cvote to strike in September
OL,6,FDrivers from six depots will walk out,
OL,7,Faccording to the union. They are:
OL,9,FWhy are union members striking?
OL,11,FUnion members rejected a two-year pay
OL,12,Fdeal that offered #1 an hour extra of
OL,13,Fpay until March 2026, then a 30p
OL,14,Fhourly increase from April 2026.
OL,16,FUnite claims that drivers are also
OL,17,Flosing out on backpay and say First
OL,18,FWest of England is not "committing to
OL,19,Fgiving any renumeration for the past
OL,20,Ffour months of the wage increase".
