OL,3,CMore than 1,000 South West bus drivers
OL,4,Cvote to strike in September
OL,6,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Fsaid: "First Group PLC can clearly
OL,8,Fafford to pay our members more, but
OL,9,Fare choosing to put profits over
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,F"This dispute is entirely of First
OL,13,FGroup's own making and any disruption
OL,14,Fcould be easily avoided. Our members
OL,15,Fwill have Unite's complete support."
