OL,3,CMore than 1,000 South West bus drivers
OL,4,Cvote to strike in September
OL,6,FDoug Claringbold, the Managing
OL,7,FDirector for First Bus in the West of
OL,8,FEngland, said: "We are disappointed
OL,9,Ffor our customers that the above
OL,10,Finflation pay offer we made to drivers
OL,11,Fhas been rejected and that they will
OL,12,Fnow face nine days of potentially
OL,13,Fsignificant disruption across Bristol,
OL,14,FBath, Wells and North Somerset.
