OL,4,Cvote to strike in September
OL,6,F"Our pay offer was significantly above
OL,7,Fthe rate of inflation and amounted to
OL,8,Fa pay increase of 8% over two years,
OL,9,Fincluding 6% this year, which was
OL,10,Frecommended by the trade union to our
OL,11,FBristol colleagues. However, that has
OL,12,Fbeen rejected and just over half of
OL,13,Four drivers have voted to strike.
