OL,3,CMore than 1,000 South West bus drivers
OL,4,Cvote to strike in September
OL,6,F"We have been committed to improving
OL,7,Fthe pay of drivers and continue to do
OL,8,Fso. Since 2021 a Bristol driver's
OL,9,Fbasic earnings has increased from just
OL,10,Fover #24,000 to more than #31,000 - a
OL,11,F31% increase. This pay offer would
OL,12,Fimmediately increase these basic
OL,13,Fearnings to over #33,000, with many
OL,14,Fdrivers earning significantly more
OL,15,Fthan this.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
