OL,3,CMore than 1,000 South West bus drivers
OL,4,Cvote to strike in September
OL,6,F"Throughout this extensive negotiation
OL,7,Fprocess, we have listened to Unite
OL,8,Fmember feedback and made a number of
OL,9,Foffers in order to try and settle this
OL,10,Fdispute, to ensure customers are not
OL,11,Faffected by strike action.
OL,13,F"Unfortunately, rather than work with
OL,14,Fus to find a resolution, Unite has
OL,15,Fdecided to press ahead with strikes in
OL,16,FSeptember at a busy time when schools
OL,17,Fand colleges are returning. We have
OL,18,Freminded them that it is our customers
OL,19,Fwho are going to suffer.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
